Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: rockchip: rk3568-anbernic-rg-ds: use ROCKNIX generic-dsi variant

Replace the in-tree RG DS device tree with the ROCKNIX variant proven to light
both 4" 640x480 panels and drive input on real hardware. The upstream
(jadard,jd9365da-h3 + adc-joystick) version is unverified on this panel lot, so
switch to the ROCKNIX generic-dsi / rocknix-singleadc-joypad layout. The matching
drivers are added in-tree by patches 0002/0003. The Makefile entry already exists
upstream.

Signed-off-by: jackheinlein <jaxxworkshop@gmail.com>

